{"lemma":"بَرْقَيْ","slug":"بَرْقَيْ","root":"ب.ر.ق","root_slug":"ب-ر-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ر-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"بَرْق","root":"برق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":5},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n2310","n2313","n2314","n2315","n2316"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to produce lightning"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to shine, to glitter, to sparkle, to flash"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of بَرَقَ (baraqa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"lightning","examples":[{"text":"أَوْ كَصَيِّبٍ مِنَ ٱلسَّمَاءِ فِيهِ ظُلُمَاتٌ وَرَعْدٌ وَبَرْقٌ يَجْعَلُونَ أَصَابِعَهُمْ فِي آذَانِهِمْ حَذَرَ ٱلْمَوْتِ […] ۝ يَكَادُ ٱلْبَرْقُ يَخْطَفُ أَبْصَارَهُمْ ۖ كُلَّمَا أَضَاءَ لَهُمْ مَشَوْا فِيهِ وَإِذَا أَظْلَمَ عَلَيْهِمْ قَامُوا"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"flash of lightning"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"telegraph"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ب ر ق (b r q). From Proto-Semitic *baraḳ- (“lightning”), although Fronzaroli states that the noun \"lightning\" may be a deverbal form, in which case only the verb would be inherited."},"ipa":["/ba.ra.qa/","/barq/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2310","headword_ar":"بَرَقَ","root":"brq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruwqN","text_ar":"بُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariyqN","text_ar":"بَرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, K,) or this is a simple subst., (S,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroqN","text_ar":"بَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqaAnN","text_ar":"بَرَقَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA, but in"},{"kind":"page_break","n":190},{"kind":"text","text":"the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruwqN","text_ar":"بُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in the S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing, Mgh, K, a sword, &c., S and the dawn, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shone, gleamed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"glistened."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also said of a cloud, aor. as above, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariyqN","text_ar":"بَرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroqF","text_ar":"بَرْقً"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqaAnN","text_ar":"بَرَقَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It gleamed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shone"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with lightning"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrq","text_ar":"ابرق","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tbr~q","text_ar":"تبرّق","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlj","text_ar":"حلج"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqati Als~amaA='u","text_ar":"بَرَقَتِ السَّمَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) aor. as above, (Msb, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqaAnN","text_ar":"بَرَقَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroqN","text_ar":"بَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruwqN","text_ar":"بُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sky lightened;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrqt","text_ar":"ابرقت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (AO, AA, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gleamed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shone"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with lightning"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lightened much"},{"kind":"text","text":"before rain; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrqt","text_ar":"ابرقت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rEd","text_ar":"رعد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqa Albaroqu","text_ar":"بَرَقَ البَرْقُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lightning appeared."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-  And [hence] said of a man, (JK, Msb, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raEada wabaraqa","text_ar":"رَعَدَ وَبَرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He threatened;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he threatened with evil;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he threatened and menaced;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he frightened"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rEd","text_ar":"رعد"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and threatened;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S in that art.;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrq","text_ar":"ابرق","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same; (JK, Msb, K;) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroEada wa A^aboraqa","text_ar":"اَرْعَدَ وَ اَبْرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or, accord. to As,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArEd","text_ar":"ارعد"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrq","text_ar":"ابرق"},{"kind":"text","text":"are not allowable. (TA, and S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rEd","text_ar":"رعد"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.) But"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqato","text_ar":"بَرَقَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroqN","text_ar":"بَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a woman, (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raEadato wa baraqato","text_ar":"رَعَدَتْ وَ بَرَقَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She beautified"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S and A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rEd","text_ar":"رعد"},{"kind":"text","text":", and K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and adorned herself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) [as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tbr~qt","text_ar":"تبرّقت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (occurring in the K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alq","text_ar":"الق"},{"kind":"text","text":", coupled with its syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazay~anat","text_ar":"تَزَيَّنَت"},{"kind":"text","text":",)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and showed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"presented, herself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rEd","text_ar":"رعد"},{"kind":"text","text":", and TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liY","text_ar":"لِى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to me:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rEd","text_ar":"رعد"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she exhibited her beauty intentionally:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"br~qt","text_ar":"برّقت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"means the same, (Lh, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taboriyqN","text_ar":"تَبْرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrqt","text_ar":"ابرقت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biwajohihaA wasaAy^iri jisomihaA","text_ar":"بِوَجْهِهَا وَسَايِرِ جِسْمِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrqt","text_ar":"ابرقت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She beautified herself in her face and the rest of her person:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano wajohihaA","text_ar":"عَنْ وَجْهِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrqt","text_ar":"ابرقت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She showed her face."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, Ibn-'Abbád, K.) ―         -b4-  Also, said of a star, or an asterism,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It rose."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA A^afoEaluhu maA baraqa Aln~ajomu fiY Als~amaA='i","text_ar":"لَا اَفْعَلُهُ مَا بَرَقَ النَّجْمُ فِى السَّمَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will not do it as long as the star,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asterism,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[by which may be meant"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the asterism of the Pleiades,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rises in the sky."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqa AlbaSaru","text_ar":"بَرَقَ البَصَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSaruhu","text_ar":"بَصَرُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The eye"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eyes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his eye"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eyes, glistened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being raised,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fixedly open:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became raised,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fixedly open:"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurring in the Kur [lxxv. 7], accord. to one reading: (Fr, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the eye,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his eye, became open by reason of fright."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariqa","text_ar":"بَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has a different meaning, which see below. (S.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqato","text_ar":"بَرَقَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a she-camel,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She put her tail between her thighs, making it to cleave to her belly, without being pregnant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she raised her tail, and feigned herself pregnant, not being so;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrqt","text_ar":"ابرقت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lh, S, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrqt bi*anbihaA","text_ar":"ابرقت بِذَنبِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrqt","text_ar":"ابرقت"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she smote with her tail at one time upon her vulva and another time upon her buttocks;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she feigned herself pregnant, not being so."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariqa","text_ar":"بَرِقَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He feared, so that he was astonished"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"amazed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stupified, at seeing the gleam of lightning:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baHira","text_ar":"بَحِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man's)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sight became confused in consequence of his looking at lightning."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in lxxv. 7.) And hence, (Bd ibid.,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariqa AlbaSaru","text_ar":"بَرِقَ البَصَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Bd,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSaruhu","text_ar":"بَصَرُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqa","text_ar":"بَرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) or the latter has [only] a meaning explained above; (S;) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqN","text_ar":"بَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is of the former verb; (S;) accord. to the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroqN","text_ar":"بَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but this is wrong; (TA;) and [of the latter verb,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruwqN","text_ar":"بُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Lh, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The eye"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eyes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his eye"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eyes, became dazzled, so as not to close,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"move, the lid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lids:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became confused, so as not to see."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariqa baSaruhu","text_ar":"بَرِقَ بَصَرُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His eye"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eyes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his sight, became weak:"},{"kind":"text","text":"whence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariqato qadamaAhu","text_ar":"بَرِقَتْ قَدَمَاهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His two feet became weak."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariqa","text_ar":"بَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"alone, (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqN","text_ar":"بَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was frightened;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he feared,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was afraid:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became confounded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perplexed, and unable to see his right course."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariqa","text_ar":"بَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a skin, aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqN","text_ar":"بَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,) so in the O, in which, as in the K, the part. n., being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariqN","text_ar":"بَرِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", indicates that the verb is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariHa","text_ar":"فَرِحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqa","text_ar":"بَرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) so in the L, (TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroqN","text_ar":"بَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruwqN","text_ar":"بُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; thus in the L, which indicates that the verb is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSara","text_ar":"نَصَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It became affected by the heat so that its butter melted and became decomposed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, JK, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and did not become compact."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqa TaEaAmFA","text_ar":"بَرَقَ طَعَامًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqahu bizayotK A^awo samonK","text_ar":"بَرَقَهُ بِزَيْتٍ اَوْ سَمْنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroqN","text_ar":"بَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruwqN","text_ar":"بُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He poured upon the food,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put into it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"somewhat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small quantity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of olive-oil"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, K) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of clarified butter."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqotu lahu","text_ar":"بَرَقْتُ لَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I made his food"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"somewhat"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"greasy for him with clarified butter."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uboruquwA AlmaA='i bizayotK","text_ar":"اُبْرُقُوا المَا=ءِ بِزَيْتٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pour ye upon the water a little olive-oil."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariqati","text_ar":"بَرِقَتِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alganamu","text_ar":"الغَنَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqN","text_ar":"بَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sheep,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats, had a complaint in their bellies from eating the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barowaq","text_ar":"بَرْوَق"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) and in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_ibilu","text_ar":"الاـِبِلُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the camels."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","K","JK","Msb","TA","As","AO","AA","Lh","Fr","IAar","Bd","L"]},{"entry_id":"n2313","headword_ar":"بَرْقٌ","root":"brq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Lightning;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what gleams in the clouds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the clouds;"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraqa","text_ar":"بَرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the first of the senses explained above], said of a thing, inf. n. ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroqN","text_ar":"بَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariyqN","text_ar":"بَرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Bd in ii. 18:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an angel's smiting the clouds, and putting them in motion, in order that they may become propelled, so that thou seest the fires"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"issue from them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Mujáhid, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a whip of light with which the angel drives the clouds:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(I'Ab, TA:) sing. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruwqN","text_ar":"بُرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e., of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"brwq","text_ar":"بروق"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the clouds: (S, K:) or it has no pl., being originally an inf. n. (Bd ubi suprà.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroqu Alxul~abi","text_ar":"بَرْقُ الخُلَّبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroqu xul~abK","text_ar":"بَرْقُ خُلَّبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroqN","text_ar":"بَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xul~abN","text_ar":"خُلَّبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lightning"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is without rain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S. [See also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xlb","text_ar":"خلب"},{"kind":"text","text":")]"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n2314","headword_ar":"بُرْقٌ","root":"brq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Lizards of the species called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DibaAb","text_ar":"ضِبَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":", pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dab~N","text_ar":"ضَبٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IAar, K.) It is app. pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baruwqN","text_ar":"بَرُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboraqu","text_ar":"اَبْرَقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": more probably, I think, of the former; from the raising of the tail, which is a habit of those lizards.]       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buroqapN","text_ar":"بُرْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n2315","headword_ar":"بَرَقٌ","root":"brq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A lamb;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamalN","text_ar":"حَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (S, K:) a Persian word, (S,) arabicized; (S, K;) originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraho","text_ar":"بَرَهْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) pl. [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buroqaAnN","text_ar":"بُرْقَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biroqaAnN","text_ar":"بِرْقَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboraAqN","text_ar":"اَبْرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n2316","headword_ar":"بَرِقٌ","root":"brq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[part. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariqa","text_ar":"بَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and particularly explained as meaning] A skin"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affected by the heat so that its butter melts and becomes decomposed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and does not become compact."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","O","K"]}]}}